---
import DocsLayout from "../layouts/DocsLayout.astro";
---

<DocsLayout title="Introduction">
    <article class="docs-content">
        <h1 class="text-6xl! mb-4!">Welcome to Gabay</h1>
        <p class="text-2xl! text-text-muted mb-12! leading-relaxed!">
            Gabay is your personal AI assistant that lives right inside
            Telegram. It connects your emails, documents, and calendar into one
            simple conversation.
        </p>

        <section class="mb-16">
            <h2 id="how-to-start" class="text-3xl! mb-8!">
                How to Get Started
            </h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-8">
                <div
                    class="flex flex-col gap-4 p-8 glass rounded-2xl border border-border-main transition-transform hover:scale-[1.02]"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand-primary/10 text-brand-primary flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 font-extrabold text-xl"
                    >
                        1
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2 text-text-main">
                            Add the Bot
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
                            Find <a
                                href="https://t.me/GabayAgentBot"
                                class="text-brand-primary font-bold hover:underline"
                                >@GabayAgentBot</a
                            > on Telegram and send a message.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="flex flex-col gap-4 p-8 glass rounded-2xl border border-border-main transition-transform hover:scale-[1.02]"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand-primary/10 text-brand-primary flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 font-extrabold text-xl"
                    >
                        2
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2 text-text-main">
                            Link Accounts
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
                            Gabay will send you a secure link. Use it to safely
                            connect your Google Workspace.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="flex flex-col gap-4 p-8 glass rounded-2xl border border-border-main transition-transform hover:scale-[1.02]"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-500 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 font-extrabold text-xl"
                    >
                        3
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2 text-text-main">
                            Start Chatting
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
                            Ask Gabay to find files, write reports, or draft
                            emails. It's that simple. ðŸš€
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <h2 id="common-tasks" class="text-3xl! mb-8!">What can I ask Gabay?</h2>
        <p class="mb-8 font-medium">
            Gabay is designed to handle the boring stuff so you don't have to.
            Try sending commands like:
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-12">
            <div
                class="p-8 glass rounded-2xl border border-border-main hover:border-brand-primary/30 transition-colors"
            >
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                    <div
                        class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-blue-500/10 flex items-center justify-center"
                    >
                        <svg
                            class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500"
                            fill="none"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            ><path
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-linejoin="round"
                                stroke-width="2"
                                d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"
                            ></path></svg
                        >
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-text-main font-bold text-lg"
                        >Find & Read</span
                    >
                </div>
                <p class="text-text-muted italic mb-2">
                    "Find any emails about my upcoming trip."
                </p>
                <p class="text-text-muted italic">
                    "What's the main takeaway from my last meeting notes?"
                </p>
            </div>

            <div
                class="p-8 glass rounded-2xl border border-border-main hover:border-emerald-500/30 transition-colors"
            >
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                    <div
                        class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500/10 flex items-center justify-center"
                    >
                        <svg
                            class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500"
                            fill="none"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            ><path
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-linejoin="round"
                                stroke-width="2"
                                d="M11 5H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v11a2 2 0 002 2h11a2 2 0 002-2v-5m-1.414-9.414a2 2 0 112.828 2.828L11.828 15H9v-2.828l8.586-8.586z"
                            ></path></svg
                        >
                    </div>
                    <span
                        class="text-text-main font-bold text-lg text-emerald-500"
                        >Create & Write</span
                    >
                </div>
                <p class="text-text-muted italic mb-2">
                    "Create a professional Google Doc about AI trends."
                </p>
                <p class="text-text-muted italic">
                    "Draft a polite reply to the email from Sarah."
                </p>
            </div>

            <div
                class="p-8 glass rounded-2xl border border-border-main hover:border-purple-500/30 transition-colors"
            >
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                    <div
                        class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-purple-500/10 flex items-center justify-center"
                    >
                        <svg
                            class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-500"
                            fill="none"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            ><path
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-linejoin="round"
                                stroke-width="2"
                                d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"
                            ></path></svg
                        >
                    </div>
                    <span
                        class="text-text-main font-bold text-lg text-purple-500"
                        >Organize</span
                    >
                </div>
                <p class="text-text-muted italic mb-2">
                    "Extract my latest Stripe invoices into a spreadsheet."
                </p>
                <p class="text-text-muted italic">
                    "Remind me to check the mail every day at 10 AM."
                </p>
            </div>

            <div
                class="p-8 glass rounded-2xl border border-border-main hover:border-amber-500/30 transition-colors"
            >
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                    <div
                        class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-amber-500/10 flex items-center justify-center"
                    >
                        <svg
                            class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-500"
                            fill="none"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            ><path
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-linejoin="round"
                                stroke-width="2"
                                d="M7 12l3-3 3 3 4-4M8 21l4-4 4 4M3 4h18M4 4h16v12a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1V4z"
                            ></path></svg
                        >
                    </div>
                    <span
                        class="text-text-main font-bold text-lg text-amber-500"
                        >Present</span
                    >
                </div>
                <p class="text-text-muted italic mb-2">
                    "Make a 7-slide deck about our marketing plan."
                </p>
                <p class="text-text-muted italic">
                    "Find 'Project Blue' and send it to my manager."
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <section
            class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-brand-primary/5 border border-brand-primary/10 mb-16"
        >
            <h2 id="safety" class="text-2xl! mb-4! border-0! pb-0!">
                Your Privacy & Safety
            </h2>
            <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-0!">
                We take security seriously. Gabay uses official "OAuth"
                connectionsâ€”this means <strong
                    >we never see your passwords</strong
                >. You have full control over what Gabay can access, and you can
                disconnect your accounts at any time with a single command.
            </p>
        </section>

        <div class="relative py-8">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center" aria-hidden="true">
                <div class="w-full border-t border-border-main"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="relative flex justify-center">
                <span
                    class="px-6 glass text-sm font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-text-muted"
                    >Developers Only</span
                >
            </div>
        </div>

        <h2 id="advanced" class="text-3xl! mb-6! mt-12!">Self-Hosting Guide</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted mb-8 text-lg">
            For technical users who want to host their own instance of Gabay.
        </p>

        <h3 id="installation" class="text-xl! mb-4!">Local Installation</h3>
        <pre class="mb-4!"><code>pip install gabay</code></pre>
        <p class="text-sm! text-text-muted mb-8!">
            Once installed, run the configuration wizard: <code
                class="text-brand-primary ml-2!">gabay config</code>
        </p>

        <h3 id="bot-setup" class="text-xl! mb-4!">
            API Keys (Telegram & Google)
        </h3>
        <p class="mb-4">
            For a private instance, you'll need the following credentials:
        </p>
        <ul
            class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 list-none! ml-0! mb-12!"
        >
            <li
                class="p-4 glass rounded-xl border border-border-main flex items-center gap-3"
            >
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-primary"></div>
                <span class="font-semibold">Bot Token from @BotFather</span>
            </li>
            <li
                class="p-4 glass rounded-xl border border-border-main flex items-center gap-3"
            >
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-primary"></div>
                <span class="font-semibold"
                    >API ID/Hash from my.telegram.org</span
                >
            </li>
            <li
                class="p-4 glass rounded-xl border border-border-main flex items-center gap-3"
            >
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-primary"></div>
                <span class="font-semibold">Gemini or Groq API Key</span>
            </li>
            <li
                class="p-4 glass rounded-xl border border-border-main flex items-center gap-3"
            >
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-primary"></div>
                <span class="font-semibold">Google Cloud OAuth Credentials</span
                >
            </li>
        </ul>

        <h3 id="google-cloud" class="text-xl! mb-4!">Google Cloud APIs</h3>
        <p class="mb-6">
            Enable these in your Google Cloud Console for full functionality:
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-16">
            <div
                class="p-4 text-center rounded-xl glass border border-border-main text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-text-muted"
            >
                Gmail API
            </div>
            <div
                class="p-4 text-center rounded-xl glass border border-border-main text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-text-muted"
            >
                Drive API
            </div>
            <div
                class="p-4 text-center rounded-xl glass border border-border-main text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-text-muted"
            >
                Docs/Slides/Sheets
            </div>
            <div
                class="p-4 text-center rounded-xl glass border border-border-main text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-text-muted"
            >
                Calendar API
            </div>
        </div>

        <h3 id="environment" class="text-xl! mb-4!">Example .env File</h3>
        <pre><code>{`# Telegram
TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN="your_token"
TELEGRAM_API_ID=12345
TELEGRAM_API_HASH="your_hash"

# Intelligence (Gemini preferred)
GEMINI_API_KEY="your_key"
LLM_PROVIDER="gemini"

# Google
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID="your_id"
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET="your_secret"`}</code></pre>
    </article>
</DocsLayout>
